{"title":"小红帽脱险记　２","authors":["梅志"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽脱险记　２"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他畏怯的停住了脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弯下腰，象打猴拳一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远的跟着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望一望，走一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"逃进了外婆的破茅屋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当面吓成了老鼠胆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转面立刻充好汉——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望不见了小红帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的勇气又回来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他伸直了腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在下面指着茅屋大声叫："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老子现在饶了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上一定要来吃掉你。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要带来一把伞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撑起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住你那些发瘟的手榴弹。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老山妖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸下了海口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就垂头丧气的走了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躲在外婆的茅屋里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越想越心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就向外婆要一把刀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他那又聋又哑的老外婆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁呀睁的，睁开了昏花的眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇摇头又摇摇手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随你怎么喊怎么叫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他依然摇摇头又摇摇手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么也不回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么也不知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有了办法，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好用手掌比着杀头的姿势"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在外婆的颈子上一擦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊呀！”外婆可吓得尖声的叫了起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但她可也懂得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就用手指一指灶台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又指一指灶台下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灶台下面的灰堆边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"果然有一把切菜刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但它锈得比泥土还更黑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用它在自己手背上割了几割，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连路路都没有划出一条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这简直比我的铅笔刀还不如！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽气愤的将它丢下了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越想越心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又向外婆要把剑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外婆用力的睁呀睁的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又睁开了她那昏花了的老眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摇摇头又摇摇手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么也不回答，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么也不知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可真气急了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向前跳进了一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做着象电影上侠客们比武一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸直一只手掌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向外婆的胸口狠狠的一刺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“啊呀！”外婆又吓了一跳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但她又马上懂得了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就用手向屋角里指了一指。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在屋角里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"左寻一寻，右找一找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算是找着了半边锈剪刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但它早已没有了尖尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连小红帽的旧裤管"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺了几下都刺不穿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这简直比我玩的小铁钉还不如！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽气愤的将它丢下了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小红帽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越想越心焦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要这"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这没有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要那"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不见。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他望着老外婆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她摇摇头又摇摇手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是睁呀睁的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁着昏花眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"到后来，她索性把眼睛一闭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自管自流着口水歪倒头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打起瞌睡来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（第一节完）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}